{"tid":1524341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［901入機場］黑警恐襲！唔使講野，入機場哂冷","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T17:58:42.000Z","uid":178163,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ac176d06056442de423cc9308d148dad98d19def","tid":1524341,"uid":178163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:02:59.000Z","msg":"網絡大軍出動<br />\n一人一Post 洗爆連登時事台 Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n繼「黑警還眼」後<br />\n901統一口號「黑警恐襲」「黑警放火」<br />\n<br />\n與其死係街頭，不如死係機場<br />\n與其街頭食彈，不如機場食彈<br />\n與其被打爆頭，不如機場爆頭<br />\n與其被打爆眼，不如機場爆眼<br />\n與其黨鐵被打，不如機鐵被打<br />\n臥底鐘意燒街，不如燒機場啦<br />\n<br />\n攬炒機場！塞爆佢，唔使講野！<br />\n901無限期塞爆機場！<br />\n<br />\n見者Copy內容開新Post洗版，唔開Post自己檢討一下良心仲係唔係到！<br />\n<br />\n出完貼要自推10下，見到其他都推下，回post都要post上面"},{"pid":"23387dedcf6f135ea34d73defa3443abcb5265a0","tid":1524341,"uid":178163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:03:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e81e9e13599d779f0570c98898cc1efbf7231b2","tid":1524341,"uid":178163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:03:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbfe26f6ba371903cc26487430994eda6b83e612","tid":1524341,"uid":178163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:03:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4b08c31b54cc96963ba5d917452c781e9bf69f0","tid":1524341,"uid":178163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:04:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16b10834901d689ea42913d5dfb0acdbe613ac31","tid":1524341,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:04:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國家級武裝恐怖份子無差別屠殺市民</span></span>"},{"pid":"8593d7f9db95a1046685e161509869c33ddd421f","tid":1524341,"uid":178163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:04:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96c7c9957a4747bf8b8a15ed0001f967e86a3d25","tid":1524341,"uid":178163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT