h=ba7711c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQL36TR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQL36TR.png&h=e3eb9cd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L2v0pFw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL2v0pFw.png&h=3a038aea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XCBfdyR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXCBfdyR.png&h=cb00c423&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ncredit to 眾多文宣巴絲<br />\n我地唔好浪費文宣巴絲們製圖嘅心血至得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好忘記今日黑警做過嘅不人道無差別毆打市民!!"}]}